  <thing id="fBlazeBerz" name="Blazing Berserker" description="When you enter your rage, your body becomes infused with fire.\n\n{b}Prerequisite{/b}: Ability to rage.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: As long as you are under the effects of a rage, you gain the fire subtype. You gain immunity to fire, but have vulnerability to cold, which means you take +50% damage from cold, regardless of whether a saving throw is allowed, or if the save is a success or failure." compset="Feat" summary="While raging you gain the fire subtype" uniqueness="useronce">
