  <thing id="fHeatEndur" name="Heat Endurance" description="Either as a result of growing up in the waste, or by training your body and mind to ignore the effects of searing heat, you can exist with ease in high-temperature environments.\n\n{b}Prerequisite{/b}: Base Fortitude save +2.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: You gain a +2 bonus on saving throws against fire effects. You can exist comfortably in temperatures up to 120&#176; F without having to make Fortitude saves (see Heat Dangers, page 12). Your protection against heat is level 1 (see Protection against Heat, page 14)." compset="Feat" summary="+2 bon to saves vs fire, no checks up to 120&#176; F, protection lvl 1 vs heat." uniqueness="useronce">
