  <thing id="fPrieWaste" name="Priest of the Wastes" description="You can swap out prepared spells for others that aid in exploring and surviving in wastelands.\n\n{b}Prerequisite{/b}: Access to the Fire, Summer&#134;, Sun, Travel, or Water domain.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: You can use a spell slot currently occupied by a prepared spell that is not a domain spell to cast a spell of equal or lower level that appears on the following list: {i}cloak of shade{/i}&#134;, {i}control weather{/i}, {i}create food and water{/i}, {i}create water{/i}, {i}endure elements{/i}, {i}heroes&#146; feast{/i}, {i}hydrate{/i}&#134;, {i}protection from dessication{/i}&#134;, {i}protection from energy{/i}, and {i}resist energy{/i}.\n&#134; New domain or spell described in Chapter 5." compset="Feat" summary="Spontaneously convert cleric spells into a small list useful in survival." uniqueness="useronce">
