  <thing id="fSandCamou" name="Sand Camouflage" description="You can hide yourself in sand with a moment&#146;s notice.\n\n{b}Prerequisites{/b}: Hide 5 ranks, Sandskimmer.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: As a standard action, you can quickly camouflage yourself in any area of ash, dust, loose earth, or sand that is at least 1 inch deep. In areas with 1 to 11 inches of appropriate loose soil, you gain a +4 bonus on Hide checks. In areas with 12 inches or more of appropriate loose soil, you instead gain a +10 bonus on Hide checks. You must still have cover or concealment to make a Hide check, as described on page 76 of the Player&#146;s Handbook." compset="Feat" summary="Stand, camou self in at least 1 in sand/ash, 1-11/12+ in +4/+10 bon to Hide." uniqueness="useronce">
