  <thing id="fSandSnare" name="Sand Snare" description="When you knock your foes into the sand, they have a hard time regaining their feet.\n\n{b}Prerequisites{/b}: Combat Expertise, Improved Trip.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: If you successfully trip an opponent in any area of ash, dust, loose earth, or sand that is at least 1 inch deep, that opponent must take a full round action to stand during the round after being tripped. Following that round, the target can get to his feet with a move action (as normal). The opponent still provokes attacks of opportunity while attempting to stand, as normal." compset="Feat" summary="If trip foe on 1+ in of ash/sand, full rd to stand on next turn, then normal." uniqueness="useronce">
