  <thing id="fScorpInst" name="Scorpion&apos;s Instincts" description="You are hard to find in the waste.\n\n{b}Prerequisites{/b}: Dex 13, Hide 5 ranks.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: You have an inborn sense of where to lurk without being seen, gaining a +2 bonus on your Hide checks and reducing the distance within which creatures can detect you by scent to 10 feet (20 feet if upwind, 5 feet if downwind). If you are in an area covered in a layer of at least 1 inch of ash, dust, loose earth, or sand, you gain an additional +2 bonus on Hide checks, a +2 bonus on Move Silently checks, and a creature can detect you by scent only if it is within 5 feet (pinpointing your location as normal)." compset="Feat" summary="Scent detects at 10 ft, 5 ft if in 1+ in ash/sand &amp; +2 to Hide &amp; Move Silent." uniqueness="useronce">
