  <thing id="fSerpFang" name="Serpent Fang" description="You are able to project your {i}ki{/i} to strike foes as though you had extended reach.\n\n{b}Prerequisite{/b}: Wis 15, Improved Unarmed Strike, Stunning Fist.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: You must declare that you are using this feat before you make your attack roll (thus, a failed attack roll ruins the attempt). By expending one Stunning Fist use for the day, you can project your {i}ki{/i} to strike an opponent that is 5 feet beyond your normal unarmed reach. If the blow hits, it deals normal unarmed damage. This feat can be used only once per round.\n\n{b}Special{/b}: Monks can use special monk weapons when using this feat, dealing damage according to the weapon." compset="Feat" summary="Use 1 stun, +5 ft to reach for next unarmed strike/monk weapon attack." uniqueness="useronce">
