  <thing id="xSureFeet" name="Sure Feet" description="Bhukas have broad feat and splayed toes that help them travel easily over sand and similar loose surfaces. They treat shallow sand as normal terrain and deep sand as shallow sand. See Sand Travel, page 18, for descriptions of shallow and deep sand." compset="Special" summary="Treat shallow sand as normal terrain and deep sand as shallow.">
