  <thing id="xGlareRes" name="Glare Resistance" description="Dark skin and long lashes around the eyes protect bhukas from sun glare (see page 18), so these creatures are never dazzled by bright sun." compset="Special" summary="Immune to sun glare, never dazzled by bright sun.">
