  <thing id="wEagleClaw" name="Eagle&apos;s Claw" description="The asheratis invented the first eagle&#146;s claw. This light, exotic melee weapon has a quarter-circle blade that is equally sharp on both the inner and outer edges. The blade is about 6 inches long and looks very much like an eagle&#146;s claw enlarged and forged in steel. The handle of an eagle&#146;s claw is slightly curved with a hole at the end to facilitate the use of a finger (middle or index) in wielding the weapon, allowing you to instantly swing the blade between differing grips. You get a +1 bonus on Sleight of Hand checks made to conceal an eagle&#146;s claw on your body (see the Sleight of Hand skill, page 81 of the Player&#146;s Handbook)." compset="Weapon">
