  <thing id="wFalchioGr" name="Falchion, Great" description="This heavy executioner&#146;s sword has the same basic profile as a falchion, albeit with a much greater blade surface. Because it is an executioner&#146;s weapon, it is often crafted as a masterwork weapon, marked with a royal seal, and created with one or more gems in the hilt." compset="Weapon">
