  <thing id="cWtWSndGlm" name="Create Sand Golem" description="You learn the secret of creating a sand golem. You do not need the Craft Golem feat to create a sand golem, as you normally would, but you cannot use this ability to create any other type of golem." compset="ClSpecial" summary="You do not need the Craft Golem feat to create a sand golem.">
