  <thing id="cWtWSndMum" name="Create Salt Mummy" description="You learn a specialized form of the ancient art of mummification. Invested with the dark power of the waste, you are able to preserve and animate a corpse. You also add to it the essence of dehydration to produce a horrid salt mummy." compset="ClSpecial" summary="You learn a specialized form of the ancient art of mummification.">
