  <thing id="cWtWDrgtGr" name="Greater Drought" description="You can produce extreme desert conditions in a 100-foot radius emanation with you at the center. The temperature band in that area rises by two steps or to severe heat, whichever produces the hotter result. You can suppress this effect for 1 round as a free action, but it renews automatically on your next turn unless you consciously suppress it again. This effect supersedes that of the local drought ability." compset="ClSpecial" summary="You can produce extreme desert conditions in a 100-foot radius emanation.">
