  <thing id="sWstStriDr" name="Waste Strider" description="The subject can move through desert environments without hindrance, ignoring movement penalties and penalties on skill checks for all types of desert and waste terrain. This spell does not grant a subject immunity to other ill effects of waste environments, such as heat and sun." compset="Spell" summary="Move through waste without penalties.">
