  <thing id="irSandstri" name="Sandstriding" description="This brass ring has the shape of a coiled rattlesnake. The wearer gains the benefit of the Sandskimmer feat (see Sandstorm p. 52).\n   Faint transmutation; CL 3rd; Forge Ring, creator must have the Sandskimmer feat or the innate ability to move easily through sand; Price 5,000gp." compset="Ring" summary="Grants the Sandskimmer feat.">
    <fieldval field="gCost" value="5000"/>
